<section class="about section-padding" aria-labelledby="AboutHeading">
  <div class="container--narrow container">
    <span class="eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow | default: 'Our story' }}</span>
    <h1 id="AboutHeading" style="margin-bottom:8px;">{{ section.settings.heading | default: 'The ones we love don’t all speak.' }}</h1>
    <p class="text-muted" style="margin-bottom:40px;max-width:560px;">{{ section.settings.intro | default: 'They become the rhythm of the house. The warm spot on the couch. The small footsteps. The quiet company through the worst of it. And then most of us have nothing on the wall to remember it by.' }}</p>

    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:var(--leading-loose);color:var(--color-ink);">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">How this started</h3>
        <p>There's a particular kind of love that doesn't always get put into words. The dog asleep at your feet while you work. The cat curled into the warmest patch of sun. The hours of small, steady company that quietly become the shape of a home.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;">We started this because the phone photo wasn't enough. The frames at the store were generic. The custom paintings online were either too expensive or too off; you could tell whoever made them hadn't really looked at the dog. Something that mattered this much deserved a place we'd actually see every day. So we built it.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">How it works</h3>
        <p>You upload one photo. You choose the look you want, soft watercolour, clean line, charcoal, modern shapes, nine ways in total. The keepsake is built from your actual pet, not stitched together from a template, and you see the entire thing before you pay a cent.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;">If it lands, we print it on museum-grade canvas or heavyweight paper and send it to your door. If it doesn't, you walk away. No one loses.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">What we care about getting right</h3>
        <p>The eyes. The set of the ears. The look that's only theirs. Most of what we make is given as a gift, whether a birthday, a homecoming, or a memorial, and we treat every order like the moment it's for.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px;">There are pets we'll never meet who get more care from us than is technically efficient, and that's the way we want it.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">Who you're talking to</h3>
        <p>A small team in Vancouver, BC. We ship across Canada, with US shipping on the way. When something goes wrong with your order, you're not filling out a form into a void. You're writing to one of us, and we'll make it right.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:48px;text-align:center;">
      <a href="/pages/create" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Create their keepsake</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Page",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "text", "id": "eyebrow", "label": "Eyebrow", "default": "Our story" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "heading", "label": "Heading", "default": "The ones we love don’t all speak." },
    { "type": "text", "id": "intro", "label": "Intro line", "default": "They become the rhythm of the house. The warm spot on the couch. The small footsteps. The quiet company through the worst of it. And then most of us have nothing on the wall to remember it by." }
  ],
  "presets": [{ "name": "About Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
